  "original_title": "\u0da9\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dbd\u0dd3\u0da7\u0dbb\u0dca 1500\u0d9a\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c 02\u0d9a\u0dca  \u0db8\u0dcf\u0da7\u0dca\u0da7\u0dd6",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "02 with 1500 liters of diesel",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The officers of Hambantota Magampura Piwasume of the Southern Expressway Interchange Police Unit have managed to arrest two suspects along with 15 barrels filled with 1500 liters of diesel that were being transported through the Southern Expressway unsafely without permits.",
        "Today (28th) around 3.30 in the morning, during the inspection of this suspicious lorry, it has been confirmed that diesel is being transported under the guise of transporting pet fish. Also, the police have observed how some packages of pet fish have been used to hide the barrels filled with diesel.",
        "The relevant diesel stock has been transported from Hambantota to Migomuwa and it has been confirmed that the relevant suspects are residents of Kochchikade and Narammala and the police said that as it is suspected that the relevant diesel stock is the fuel stock supplied to Dhiwara vessels in the Hambantota season, an investigation has been started to find the matter.",
        "The relevant diesel stock, the suspects and the lorry are scheduled to be presented to the Hambantota court."
      ],
